<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 07 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="7" arg="0x1010 0x1100 0xcd00" /></message>
	<message label="016" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你想問我為什麼不撐傘？<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為，我總覺得每一場雨<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
都有女性在某處獨自悲泣，<delay40 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以才想用全身去承受那份悲傷啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="017" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="017_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我覺得即使是下雨天，<delay20 />
也不見得都只有令人討厭的事喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />例如說，<delay8 />這下雨的聲音<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不僅能夠讓人感到平靜，<delay20 />
也能使心情變得祥和喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="017_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay8 />
是雨天讓你感到憂鬱嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過下雨也是有好處的喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比方說……當你心裡難受的時候，<delay20 />
雨滴會幫你抹去淚痕，對吧？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />與你心中的那份悲傷一起<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="017_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />下雨的時候，<delay20 />
樹木與花草們會發出沙沙聲響，<delay20 />
聽起來就像在聊天呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然我無法理解她們的語言，<delay20 />
但應該是在聊<delay20 />
關於<tag a="110" b="10" />的事情吧～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="018" attrib="00 00 00 09 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="018_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我覺得純潔的心就像白雪一樣，<delay40 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />都潔白無瑕、一塵不染啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="018_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="31" arg="0x6e 0x6f" /></message>
	<message label="110" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="8" />被染成一片銀白，<delay20 />
氣氛也變得跟平常不同呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就像是被施了魔法一樣<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="111" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這場雪下完以後，不知道會不會有積雪？<10_4 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果有的話……重返童心玩玩雪，<delay20 />
或許也不錯呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="018_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大雪紛飛，<delay20 />
簡直像是要掩蓋日常的風景<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果在名為<tag a="110" b="8" />的畫布<delay20 />
抹上名為<tag a="110" b="10" />的顏色，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看起來會是什麼樣子呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="019" attrib="00 00 00 0a 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然雪飄落到地上就會變髒，<delay20 />
但在空中飛舞時真的很美呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就像你的心一樣<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Surprised" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，這雪是不是下得太大啦！？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="020" attrib="00 00 00 05 00 0a 00 00"><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />遇到像今天這樣的好天氣，<delay8 />
就會很想跑出去玩呢～！<pageBreak /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />即使早上的新聞說了<delay frames="40" />
我今天的運勢非常差<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="022" attrib="00 00 00 06 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="022_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說起來，今天的天色<delay20 />
看起來真是難以揣測呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就像女孩子的心意一樣<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="022_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />天空看起來似乎隨時都會哭泣呢。<10_4 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這世界上的某處，<delay20 />
是否有個女孩正在傷心難過呢？<pageBreak /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />無論何時我都會陪在你身旁的。<delay frames="40" />
來，<delay20 />儘管哭吧！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊<tag a="110" b="0" />抱歉，<delay20 />不小心就開始胡思亂想了。</message>
	<message label="022_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵，<delay20 />別擔心。<10_4 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總有一天會放晴的，<delay20 />因為心裡的悲傷與天氣<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />都不會永遠不變<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="021" attrib="00 00 00 0b 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像今天這種落英繽紛的日子，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />非常適合跳支舞呢～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="023" attrib="18 00 00 01 00 09 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
這麼晚了，你卻獨自出門散步嗎？</message>
	<message label="024" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="024_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也是喔。<delay20 />
夜晚的風<delay20 />邀請我出來走走<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />或許<tag a="110" b="8" />的大自然
是在不著痕跡地暗示我<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />現在可以遇到你呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="024_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也是喔。<delay20 />
總覺得現在睡覺還太早了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果一邊哼著<tag a="135" b="4" arg="0xcd00" />一邊散步，<delay20 />
或許就能看到<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在日常中<delay8 />難得一見的風景喔。</message>
	<message label="024_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />當我想獨自沉思時，<delay20 />
便會覺得這時的寂靜<delay8 />特別美好呢～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="025" attrib="1a 00 00 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay8 />
如果你有什麼煩惱，<delay20 />
無論何時都歡迎來找我商量喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />例如<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />世界上<delay20 />有太多可愛的女孩子，<delay8 />
所以很煩惱之類的<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="026" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="12" arg="0x1b 0x1c" /></message>
	<message label="027" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以總是讓我有
Romance即將來臨的預感。<delay frames="40" />
雖然一直都還是沒來呢，<delay frames="40" /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哈哈～！</message>
	<message label="028" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你說那是我的煩惱？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵，<delay20 />沒有錯<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />現在在我眼前的你也是，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="029" attrib="1e 00 00 05 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Dance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天天氣很棒耶！<10_4 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />簡直超級適合洗衣服～</message>
	<message label="030" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="030_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在下次約會之前，<delay20 />
我想把自己的決勝服裝送洗。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然還沒有約會的預定就是了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="030_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">對了，<tag a="110" b="4" />。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你對洗衣服這件事有什麼堅持嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我一定會讓待洗的衣服們<delay20 />
聽<tag a="135" b="4" arg="0xcd00" />的名曲喔。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然沒有什麼特別的意義就是了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="030_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你喜歡哪種香味的洗衣精呢？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我推薦新鮮的<tag a="135" b="2" arg="0xcd00" />香味喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="031" attrib="20 00 00 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />喜歡<delay20 />什麼樣的天氣呢？<10_4 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我是看心情而定，沒有一個標準啦<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="032" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="032_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />現在的心情……應該是晴天吧。<delay frames="40" />
看著風光明媚的天空，<delay20 />
果然就能讓心情變得舒暢呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="032_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />現在的心情……應該是雨天吧。<delay frames="40" />
聽說由大自然的聲音所勾勒出的節奏<delay20 />
擁有治癒人心的效果喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />下雨天時會有睡意，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />或許就是因為<delay8 />被那神祕而魅人的
Melody所圍繞吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="032_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />現在的心情……應該是下雪吧。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我喜歡平日習以為常的風景<delay20 />
彷彿化為奇幻世界的瞬間，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你看天空！<10_4 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />令人心情舒暢的萬里晴空<delay8 />
就在我們眼前呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感覺今晚的星空，<delay20 />
會像在<delay8 />360度的環景螢幕上<delay8 />
映照出無數散落的寶石般喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="20" />如果能與你一起欣賞<delay8 />
這麼浪漫的景色，<delay20 />
感覺一定很棒<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />天氣這麼好，會讓人很Happy呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在今天這樣的日子裡，<delay8 />
就連星星也會特別耀眼吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay8 /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />
如果能看見流星，<delay20 />你會許下什麼願望呢？</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="1" arg="0xc9 0xca 0xcb" /></message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你抬頭看看天空，<delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="4" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是閃耀著七色光芒的彩虹喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />簡直就像在童話中出現的<delay20 />
魔法之橋呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="20" />呵呵呵<tag a="110" b="0" />橋的另一邊<delay20 />
是通往什麼樣的地方呢<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay8 />
你快看<tag a="110" b="8" />的天空～！<delay20 />
有兩道彩虹呢～！<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="20" />這就是所謂的Double rainbow啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
據說幸運會降臨在<delay20 />
看見兩道彩虹的人身上<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過光是能和你一起欣賞兩道彩虹，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就非常高興了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><delay frames="18" />雖然今天天氣很好，空氣很清新，<delay20 />
<anim id="ColdChill" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但總覺得有點冷呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在這種日子裡，我會有種預感。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那就是在<tag a="110" b="8" />的天空上<delay8 />
將會出現<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />極光喔。</message>
	<message label="107" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，你抬頭看看<delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="8" />的天空<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />飄舞在夜空中的光之帷幕，<delay20 />
那就是極光喔！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />十分神祕美麗吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="90" b="27" />年<tag a="90" b="28" />月<tag a="90" b="29" />日<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />與你一同仰望天空的這一天<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我會<delay20 />永遠記得的。</message>
	<message label="108" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="12" />好不容易能見到你，<delay20 />
卻因為這場霧，<delay8 />
而讓我看不清你的身影～<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果可以的話，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真想再靠近你一點，感受你的溫暖。<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我亂說的啦，<delay8 />哈哈～！<delay20 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="109" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天的天空<delay20 />
還真不平靜呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果你會害怕打雷的聲音，<delay8 />
不用害羞，<delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />儘管飛向<tag a="110" b="10" />的懷裡吧<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果你也想許願，<delay20 />
現在就是最佳時機喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />劃過天際的Shooting star<delay20 />
可是不等人的喔。<delay frames="30" />
簡直就像是<delay20 />變幻莫測的人心<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，在我顧著說話的時候，<delay20 />
消失不見了呢，<delay frames="30" /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哈哈！<delay20 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="12" />因為今天天氣很好，<delay20 />
所以我整天都想著，<delay20 />
希望有機會和你一起看流星群<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我真是Lucky<tag a="110" b="15" />喔。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為在向流星許願之前，<delay20 />
我的願望就實現啦，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="203" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你許願了嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />用<colour id="1" />操控搖桿<colour id="65535" />仰望天空，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在流星劃過天際時按下<colour id="1" /><colour id="65535" />的話，<delay8 />
就能夠許願了喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="16" />不過不可以因為有很多流星，<delay20 />就太貪心呢。
許願越是集中，
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />才越有機會上達天聽喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>